          "intro": "Cookie spread is the main variable to control.",
          "items": [
            {
              "fix": "Chill the dough for longer before baking. Make sure the melted butter has cooled before mixing.",
              "cause": "Dough too warm, or butter still hot when the eggs were added.",
              "symptom": "Cookies spread too much and thin out."
